      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And the few spammers who have stolen my email and won’t let go, incessantly sending me garbage each week?",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Same story",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
