          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Marketers (some of them, anyway) have somehow convinced themselves that my attention is so conformable (and invaluable) that—if they just continue to poke and prod—eventually I’ll let up. I’ll use their service, buy their product, make those years of incessant goading inevitably pay off.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Not likely.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Attention is far too scarce a resource than to ceaselessly waste it. In fact, the more you do, the",
          "marks": []
